Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.41,0:00:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As times change, difficult\Ncases increase in number!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.12,0:00:06.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Today's a lodge mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:08.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the mysterious bandaged man?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.25,0:00:11.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sees the single truth\Nfor what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.21,0:00:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and looks like a kid\Nbut has the mind of an adult!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.42,0:00:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.71,0:01:52.09,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,The Mountain Lodge Bandage\NMan Murder Case (Part 1).
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.00,0:01:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? That's strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:02:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The lodge should be\Nright around here...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:04.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, we're not lost, are we?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.26,0:02:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eep...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.35,0:02:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.52,0:02:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just taking\Na little side trip!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're here!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.36,0:02:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.70,0:02:22.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Someone's walking...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.33,0:02:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's going\Nto the lodge too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.63,0:02:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if he's going\Nto the lodge too?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.55,0:02:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think so...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.80,0:02:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Ran!\NWhat were you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.34,0:02:43.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.76,0:02:47.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm nice enough to let you stay\Nat my family's lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.22,0:02:48.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and you show up late...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.73,0:02:51.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured you'd bring him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.31,0:02:53.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should be more\Nconsiderate, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.23,0:02:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if you're one to talk...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.90,0:03:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep hanging around this twerp\Nand you'll never fall in love!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.86,0:03:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Love?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:07.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're here to meet\Nsome wonderful guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.41,0:03:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with nature all around us,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have dream-like\Nromances with them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.33,0:03:17.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah, I forgot she's\Nthat kind of person...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.34,0:03:22.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? These "wonderful guys"\Naren't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.43,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.84,0:03:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My sister's friends\Ngot here long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and are relaxing in their rooms.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.27,0:03:34.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That reminds me, is one of their\Nfaces wrapped in bandages?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:36.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bandages? No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.69,0:03:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of the people here are hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we just saw--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.03,0:03:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe he lives nearby, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:47.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, stop being a weirdo\Nand put your stuff away!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You guys' room is upstairs!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.08,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, look at all\Nthese rooms up here...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:01.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which one is ours?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:05.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! My mistake!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go!\NThis is ours, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.86,0:04:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Geez, learn to knock\Nbefore opening doors!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.12,0:04:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're all from the same circle?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.58,0:04:35.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! They all made films together\Nduring my sister's college days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.87,0:04:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The five closest people got\Ntogether for the first time in two years!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to Ran is Ota-{\i1}san{\i0},
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.01,0:04:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who usually played the leading role!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.22,0:04:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.22,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next to him is Sumiya-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nour cameraman!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.76,0:04:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiya!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.68,0:04:52.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our stage manager,\NTakahashi-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.39,0:04:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.06,0:04:57.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.10,0:04:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What did you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.86,0:05:00.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing really...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.90,0:05:06.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up is our makeup\Nand wardrobe person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.20,0:05:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,my sister, who is also\Nlooking for a husband!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.83,0:05:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.91,0:05:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And last is our director,\Nscriptwriter, and club president--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.79,0:05:16.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikeda Chikako-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.67,0:05:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same Ikeda Chikako-{\i1}san {\i0}who wrote\Nthe very latest movie, "Blue Kingdom"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.34,0:05:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:29.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She wrote it during college\Nand it started her career, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.26,0:05:31.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag up old stories like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hear there's talk\Nabout your next movie...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:39.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ikeda-{\i1}sensei{\i0}! How about\Na word for your fans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.02,0:05:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop being silly, Sumiya-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.90,0:05:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still love to tape things, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.40,0:05:47.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I can't kick the habit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.95,0:05:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takahashi!\NHave you gotten fatter?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.24,0:05:54.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I guess I'm about\N100 kilograms now...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.95,0:05:56.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get you in frame anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.91,0:05:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I bet!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This certainly brings back\Nmemories of college!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.05,0:06:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Atsuko...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.63,0:06:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure she'd be here now\Nif she hadn't done that...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:13.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Atsuko?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.10,0:06:17.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not talk about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:19.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I took time out of my\Nbusy schedule to be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's not talk about someone\Nwho died two years ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.61,0:06:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Celebrities sure do\Nsay strange things...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's that mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:35.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.33,0:06:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go make dinner now,\Nso just make yourselves at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.12,0:06:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, I'll go\Nfinish fixing the roof!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.46,0:06:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They said it was going\Nto rain this evening!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd appreciate that,\NTakahashi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.80,0:06:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.05,0:06:49.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.14,0:06:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sounds like the perfect\Nkind of work for a set designer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you say\Nthe rest of us play cards?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.52,0:06:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I'll play!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.19,0:07:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where're you going, Chikako?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.03,0:07:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi said it's gonna rain!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.12,0:07:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really coming down...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no enjoying the view now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.26,0:07:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.05,0:07:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't he dreamy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:41.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's like so cool and suave--\Ntotally my type!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.31,0:07:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's right,\Nyou have Shinichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bad he couldn't\Ncome with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As if! I'd bust him upside\Nthe head if he were here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.16,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say. Would you like\Nto take a walk with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.20,0:08:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, you're not\Ndoing anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.21,0:08:09.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it's raining outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Walks in the rain\Ncan be invigorating.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.63,0:08:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.93,0:08:17.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.89,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She'll pay!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.02,0:08:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That lousy Ran!\NShe has Shinichi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.78,0:08:32.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.95,0:08:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll steal Shinichi-{\i1}kun {\i0}from her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:36.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No. No, you won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.62,0:08:39.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? There's someone you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.58,0:08:40.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.45,0:08:43.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you don't know\Nwhen he'll be back, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:46.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You should dump\Nthe cold-hearted jerk
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.08,0:08:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and find a better man!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.09,0:08:51.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How about I teach you...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.76,0:08:55.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...what adult love is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.68,0:08:57.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.43,0:09:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lightning!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.60,0:09:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.48,0:09:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, that was\Na really close one!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.44,0:09:14.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! They're gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.32,0:09:18.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.24,0:09:19.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might be lost...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.71,0:09:30.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ota-{\i1}san{\i0}, where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.63,0:09:33.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say something if you're there!\NOta-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.72,0:09:43.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.48,0:09:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.49,0:09:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you screaming about--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.03,0:10:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.53,0:10:02.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.33,0:10:04.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A man in bandages?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.08,0:10:08.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! He attacked\NRan in the forest!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.25,0:10:09.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You serious?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.54,0:10:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? You guys didn't see him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.29,0:10:14.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't the three of you\Nin the forest too?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.41,0:10:18.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just went looking for Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.82,0:10:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't see anything like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.84,0:10:23.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't see him either,\Nright, Chikako?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.01,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.18,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You went and disappeared\Nsomewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.85,0:10:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I went to get an umbrella!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.35,0:10:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you sure you weren't\Nafraid of the lightning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.69,0:10:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.86,0:10:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:36.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's almost over\Nbetween them...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, did you see the guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He ran toward the lodge...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:48.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I didn't see anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see him, Takahashi-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.42,0:10:52.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was on the roof\Nthe entire time,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.92,0:10:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't remember\Nseeing anyone like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.46,0:11:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I did see someone\Nstrange by the bridge
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.43,0:11:03.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when I first got here...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.47,0:11:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't really see his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.22,0:11:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but he was wearing\Na black cape and a hood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.94,0:11:13.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! That's the person\Nwho attacked me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.61,0:11:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.65,0:11:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw the same guy\Nwhen I got here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.74,0:11:22.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here! But I figured\Nhe lived nearby...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.36,0:11:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That can't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two or three lodges\Non the other side of the bridge,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.08,0:11:30.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and there's a mountain on this side...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who was that guy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.08,0:11:34.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We should call the police!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.46,0:11:35.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.38,0:11:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? The phone's not working?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:45.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But it was working this afternoon...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe the phones are down\Nbecause of that lightning strike?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.77,0:11:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was him! That\Nbandaged man cut the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.11,0:11:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.82,0:11:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.95,0:12:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.76,0:12:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge is out!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.48,0:12:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bridge is out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.86,0:12:24.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably fell on its own.\NIt was pretty old.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.90,0:12:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.44,0:12:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone cut it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.95,0:12:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at this bridge support.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.62,0:12:36.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?!\NIt's been chopped up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.91,0:12:39.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somebody used some sort of blade...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.75,0:12:42.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who on earth would do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.32,0:12:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was that guy!\NHe did this too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.71,0:12:46.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.88,0:12:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This "bandaged man" is ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.72,0:12:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He attacked the girl in\Nthe forest, cut the phone line,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.76,0:12:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and chopped the bridge down because\Nhe enjoys watching us get scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.97,0:12:58.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we keep getting afraid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll be giving him what he wants!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.52,0:13:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.61,0:13:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, it's dark out,\Nso our only choice
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.48,0:13:10.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,is to wait until\Ntomorrow morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.53,0:13:15.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus this "bandaged man"\Neveryone's worked up about
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.08,0:13:17.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,might still be hiding in the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.33,0:13:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.41,0:13:19.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.54,0:13:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.71,0:13:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to bed now.\NI'm suddenly tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't need any dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.34,0:13:35.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.11,0:13:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for making you help, Ran-{\i1}chan{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.11,0:13:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No problem!\NI always do this at home!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a reunion\Nthis has turned into...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.99,0:13:56.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone's suddenly unsociable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:59.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all because you\Nmentioned that incident!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.90,0:14:02.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean about Atsuko-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.33,0:14:06.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl that had something\Nhappen two years ago--
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She killed herself.\NTwo years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.30,0:14:15.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a member\Nof our filmmaking group, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.80,0:14:18.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then she suddenly\Nhanged herself in her room,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.64,0:14:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone stopped\Nmeeting after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.56,0:14:23.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were all so close, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.52,0:14:29.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I asked everyone here\Nfor a long-overdue reunion!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.98,0:14:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So let's not talk about\Nthat anymore, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.32,0:14:34.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.36,0:14:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, I'm starving.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.20,0:14:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Where's Chikako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.66,0:14:40.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She went to bed early.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.91,0:14:43.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Takahashi-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Dinner's ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.37,0:14:45.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be down in a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.21,0:14:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Is the roof fixed?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.33,0:14:48.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, for the most part.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.96,0:14:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Smile, you two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get down here, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.26,0:14:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The food's gonna get cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.80,0:14:58.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.39,0:15:01.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who're you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.18,0:15:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.22,0:15:04.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's someone\Nby the downstairs window!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.06,0:15:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the window?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.61,0:15:17.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! It's too dark\Nto see where they went!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.24,0:15:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.83,0:15:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright! Let's follow the kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:26.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lock the doors and wait here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.08,0:15:28.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, Takahashi!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.17,0:15:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Me, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:29.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.13,0:15:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.26,0:15:42.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.81,0:15:44.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me it's Chikako's?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:48.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's an arm over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.77,0:15:51.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell's goin' on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.27,0:15:53.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's split up and look!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.61,0:15:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako! Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.65,0:15:58.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako! Where are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:10.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako! Say something! Chikako!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.84,0:16:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako was?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.51,0:16:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, she had been murdered...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.39,0:16:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...by the time we got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.77,0:16:27.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.60,0:16:29.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For now, we covered\Nthe body with my jacket
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.69,0:16:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and left it in the forest...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.52,0:16:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would someone\Nkill Chikako-{\i1}san{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.52,0:16:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.69,0:16:39.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If only I hadn't\Nplanned this reunion,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.03,0:16:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'd still be--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.49,0:16:44.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true, Ayako!\NIt's not your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.66,0:16:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bandaged man is to blame!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.95,0:16:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That crazed murderer\Nwho ran off with Chikako
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.96,0:16:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,before our very eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do we do if he comes back?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.01,0:17:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be fine if we\Nlock the place down.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.97,0:17:05.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako was careless enough\Nto stroll around outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.18,0:17:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's forget about this\Nand get some shut-eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:11.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ota! How can you--
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.65,0:17:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right. It's getting late.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.40,0:17:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make sure everything\Nis locked and get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll climb down the mountain\Nand get the police tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.41,0:17:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Front door's locked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.04,0:17:32.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left is our rooms...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.25,0:17:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.90,0:17:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako-{\i1}san{\i0}'s slippers aren't here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.86,0:17:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Slippers?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.59,0:17:43.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If she went out the front door,\Nher slippers should be here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.13,0:17:46.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She might not have left from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:48.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.22,0:17:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What if the guy\Nsnuck into the lodge
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.73,0:17:53.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and attacked Chikako-{\i1}san {\i0}upstairs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.44,0:17:55.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course he didn't, Sonoko!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.52,0:17:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember? When Conan-{\i1}kun\N{\i0}and the others ran after him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.73,0:18:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you, me, and Ayako-{\i1}san {\i0}split up\Nand checked all the locks!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.91,0:18:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Chikako-{\i1}san{\i0}'s room\Nwasn't in shambles,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.95,0:18:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and the window was\Nlocked from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.58,0:18:15.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm almost certain she went outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.38,0:18:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, she was wearing shoes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.09,0:18:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her leg had been\Nchopped off, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.76,0:18:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.13,0:18:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, does this lodge\Nhave any other exits?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.30,0:18:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. The back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.31,0:18:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A back door?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:33.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go! These are definitely\NChikako-{\i1}san{\i0}'s slippers!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.11,0:18:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We didn't leave\Nany spare ones out!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.99,0:18:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means Chikako-{\i1}san\N{\i0}went out this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.41,0:18:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, probably.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.53,0:18:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why did she go out this way\Nand not the front door?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.45,0:18:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost like she was trying\Nto sneak out unseen...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.62,0:18:58.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, it's really muddy here--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.29,0:18:59.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,has someone been using this door?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.79,0:19:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was probably my sister;
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.71,0:19:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the gas switch and stuff\Nis in the backyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.42,0:19:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we found her slippers,\Nso let's go to bed now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.30,0:19:08.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.94,0:19:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There! Now our room's\Nokay too, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.61,0:19:23.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.94,0:19:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop worrying,\Neverything'll be all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.95,0:19:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the bandaged man\Nshows up again,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.87,0:19:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat him up with my karate!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.58,0:19:33.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.04,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, right! When he attacked you in the\Nforest you were too scared to do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, why do you think\Nhe attacked you, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.00,0:19:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.\NMaybe it didn't matter who.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.67,0:19:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, Ran-neechan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.05,0:19:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does anybody have\Na grudge against you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.84,0:19:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Like anyone whose face\Nyou injured with karate?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.09,0:19:57.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now go to sleep!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.19,0:19:58.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.73,0:20:06.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But there's something odd\Nabout that bandaged man.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he took Chikako-{\i1}san{\i0},\Nwho left out the back door,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.49,0:20:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then why would he go around\Nto the front door for us to see?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To make us afraid? Or perhaps--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.25,0:20:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.83,0:20:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sleep with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.28,0:20:24.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What for?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.21,0:20:27.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because you're afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.63,0:20:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just because.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.97,0:20:31.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sweet dreams, Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:34.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls have some nerve!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.97,0:20:37.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now where was I?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That bandaged man had just--
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.40,0:20:43.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I was saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.73,0:20:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I can't think!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.07,0:20:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, this is a crazed\Nmurderer we're dealing with;
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,this is a job\Nfor the police, not me...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time for sleep...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.33,0:20:57.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I sleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.99,0:22:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's after Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.74,0:22:59.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.60,0:23:01.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.49,0:23:02.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.58,0:23:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.92,0:23:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! I sprained my ankle!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.88,0:23:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once Ran falls asleep,\Nthere's no waking her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.30,0:23:14.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anything around here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.63,0:23:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it!\NThe Voice-Altering Bow Tie!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.18,0:23:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll crank up the volume, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.79,0:23:22.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get up!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.90,0:23:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ran! Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!\NWhat's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.66,0:23:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Open the door! Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.52,0:23:44.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.50,0:23:46.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Conan-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.00,0:23:49.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.79,0:23:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he after Ran?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.27,0:24:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The bandaged man is after Ran!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.27,0:24:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But why her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.55,0:24:11.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something's nagging at me...
